column_description: Primary key uniquely identifying each car in the `cars_data` table
Miles per gallon, representing the fuel efficiency of the car (can be null if data is missing)
Number of cylinders in the car's engine
Engine displacement, representing the total volume of all the cylinders in the engine (in liters)
Power output of the car's engine (can be null if data is missing)
Weight of the car in pounds
Time taken for the car to accelerate from 0 to 60 mph (in seconds)
